description: A dashboard for visualizing results from the k6.io load testing tool, using the InfluxDB exporter

targets.query: SELECT sum("value") FROM "http_reqs" WHERE $timeFilter AND "expected_response" = 'true' GROUP BY time(1s) fill(null)
SELECT sum("value") FROM "http_reqs" WHERE $timeFilter AND "expected_response" = 'true' GROUP BY time(1s) fill(null)
SELECT sum("value") FROM "http_reqs" WHERE $timeFilter AND "expected_response" = 'true' GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT sum("value") FROM "checks" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "check" fill(none)
SELECT count("value") FROM "errors" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT distinct(url) AS Request FROM "http_req_failed" WHERE "value"=1 AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "name"
SELECT count(url) AS Errors FROM "http_req_failed" WHERE "value"=1 AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "name"
SELECT max("value") FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT percentile("value", 95) FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT percentile("value", 90) FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT min("value") FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)

title: K6 Tests Report
